The full system scaffold for upgrading the CRISPR-Cas9 project has been created. It includes:

A Rust-based DNA Simulation Engine

Python-based AI genome strategist and mutation forecasting

A Cas9 Virtual Assistant powered by LLMs

A WebGL genome UI

A Rust orchestrator to tie all services together


Let me know if you want:

Starter code for any of the modules

Integration logic between Python and Rust

Deployment setup (Docker, Compose, etc.)

An interactive terminal or CLI for control